AuctionCreated(uint256).details: emitted when an auction created {auctionId} is the number of auction

AuctionEndTimeIncreased(uint256,uint256).details: emmited when a bid take apart less than 10 minutes to end of auction by {bidder} {newAuctionEndTime} is old auction end time plus 10 minutes

AuctionEnded(uint256,uint256).details: emiited when auctions {auctionId} for tree {treeId} finisehd. {winner} is the final bidder of auction and {amount} is the auction's highestBid

AuctionWithdrawFaild(uint256,address,uin.details: emitted when automatic withdraw of older bid fail {auctionId} is id of auction and {bidder} is the old bidder to charge automatically with  amount {amount}

HighestBidIncreased(uint256,uint256,addr.details: emitted when highestBid for auctions {auctionid} and tree {treeID} increase by {bidder} with value of {amount}

bid(uint256).details: bid to auctions {_auctionId}  by user in a time beetwen start time and end time of auction and return the old bidder's amount to account NOTE its require to send at least {higestBid + bidInterval } value. NOTE check if less than 10 minutes left to end of auction add 10 minutes to the end date of auction emit a {HighestBidIncreased} event

createAuction(uint256,uint64,uint64,uint.details: create an auction for {_treeId} with strating date of {_startDate} and ending date of {_endDate} and initialPrice of {_initialPrice} and bidInterval of {_bidInterval} NOTE its necessary that a fundDestributionModel has been assigned to {_treeId} NOTE after create an auction for a tree provideStatus set to 1 NOTE for creating an auction for a tree the provideStatus of tree must be 0

endAuction(uint256).details: everyone can call this method after auction end time and if auction have bidder , transfer owner of tree to bidder and fund tree. NOTE auction status set to end here emit a {AuctionEnded} event

returns._0: true in case of TreeAuction contract have been initialized

manualWithdraw().details: accounts that not funded while automatic withdraw in bid can manually withdraw

returns._0: true in case of seccussful withdraw and false otherwise
